Package org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.tests.engine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    _Suite
    Suite to run all JUnit tests in this package: org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.tests.engine All tests are run "as-is", just as if they were run individually.
    Derby6396Test
    Regression test case for DERBY-6396.
    ErrorStreamTest
    Tests related to the Derby error stream.
    LockInterruptTest
    Test that other threads are able to proceed if one thread is interrupted when it's waiting for a lock.
    ModuleLoadingTest
    This class contains tests for correct loading (booting) of modules and factories.
    ReadMeFilesTest
    Tests related to the 3 Derby readme files.
    RestrictiveFilePermissionsTest
    Tests related to use of restrictive file permissions (DERBY-5363).
    ShutdownWithoutDeregisterPermissionTest
    Test that shutdown works even if derby.jar does not have permission to deregister the JDBC driver.
